snippet.textDisplay:
Billy ailish May your angel save you from harm
And protect from lies and evil people,
And don't let fate throw a stone at your back,
And warm with his grace.

May the days to come not be a burden,
And life doesn't throw you out of the saddle.
In the soul-peace, harmony and joy,
Love and a spark of God's warmth...

Let all dreams come true,
And there will be less grief and loss;
Fate-as often as possible smiled
And if necessary, he opened the door.

Always in yourself let faith be firm,
Reliable and honest friends,
In all matters and purposes - a sense of proportion:
After all, you can't justify everything with risk...

May your faithful angel protect you
And closes the wing from trouble...
